          <FONT FACE="verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE=2> <B>What about jumping to the beginning of a command?</B> (<A HREF="/comments/2004/3/9/16838/14935/90?mode=alone;showrate=1#90">3.00 / 6</A>) (<A CLASS="light" HREF="/comments/2004/3/9/16838/14935/90#90">#90</A>)  </FONT> <BR>
          <FONT FACE="verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE=2>by <A HREF="/user/uid:27001">frankwork</a> on Wed Mar 10, 2004 at 09:26:51 PM EST<BR> </FONT>
