          <FONT FACE="verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE=2> <B>More .screenrc fun</B> (<A HREF="/comments/2004/3/9/16838/14935/121?mode=alone;showrate=1#121">3.00 / 7</A>) (<A CLASS="light" HREF="/comments/2004/3/9/16838/14935/121#121">#121</A>)  </FONT> <BR>
