          <FONT FACE="verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE=2> <B>Yet more screen tricks.</B> (<A HREF="/comments/2004/3/9/16838/14935/148?mode=alone;showrate=1#148">3.00 / 7</A>) (<A CLASS="light" HREF="/comments/2004/3/9/16838/14935/148#148">#148</A>)  </FONT> <BR>
          <FONT FACE="verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE=2>by <A HREF="/user/uid:301">static</a> on Thu Mar 11, 2004 at 09:53:29 PM EST<BR> </FONT>
