          <FONT FACE="verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE=2> <B>Trick for transfering files using only terminal.</B> (<A HREF="/comments/2004/3/9/16838/14935/173?mode=alone;showrate=1#173">3.00 / 5</A>) (<A CLASS="light" HREF="/comments/2004/3/9/16838/14935/173#173">#173</A>)  </FONT> <BR>
