          <FONT FACE="verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE=2> <B>Kinda sorta like gnuserv</B> (<A HREF="/comments/2004/3/9/16838/14935/179?mode=alone;showrate=1#179">none / 0</A>) (<A CLASS="light" HREF="/comments/2004/3/9/16838/14935/179#179">#179</A>)  </FONT> <BR>
