          <FONT FACE="verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE=2> <B>screen is essential for heavy irc use</B> (<A HREF="/comments/2004/3/9/16838/14935/189?mode=alone;showrate=1#189">none / 0</A>) (<A CLASS="light" HREF="/comments/2004/3/9/16838/14935/189#189">#189</A>)  </FONT> <BR>
          <FONT FACE="verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE=2>by <A HREF="/user/uid:34756">akuzi</a> on Thu Apr 01, 2004 at 06:45:32 PM EST<BR> </FONT>
