    <FONT FACE="verdana, arial, helvetica, sans-serif" SIZE=2> I absolutely loved screen back in my university days. &nbsp;I would be hacking at the lab at school until it was late enough that I wanted to go home. &nbsp;Then I would just detach my screen, go home, login and reattach the screen and I would be right back in the same place. &nbsp;Sadly I don't find much use for it these days. <BR>... --- ...<BR> </FONT>
